item.title: Mr. Orange-summon- trivia
item.content:encoded:
Mr.orange seems to be based off of Jeremiah Gottwald, from code geass. http://codegeass.wikia.com/wiki/Orange-kun

He was sorta framed by zero by being called orange-kun (plain orange in English) and then forced to help him and a captive escape publicly by using his power of the Geass.
